requestBody.description:
Provide one of: studyUUID, studyID, or protocolID.
The scenario-identifying data (scenarioUUID, scenarioID) can be omitted if there is an active scenario to which the data is to be pushed.
Provide one of: siteGroupUUID or siteGroupID (e.g. US, FR).
Randomization Group data (randomizationGroupUUID, randomizationGroupID) can be omitted if the study has exactly one randomization group.
Treatment Group data (treatmentGroupUUID, treatmentGroupID) is optional. If not provided, enrollment is considered to be randomization group level.
Provide one of enrollmentDate (UTC ISO date of Monday of the week) or enrollmentWeekDate (ISO week format).
enrollmentValue (5 decimal places, e.g.123.12345) is mandatory.
If you provide more than one value to identify Study, Scenario, Randomization Group, Treatment group, or Enrollment (Week) Date, the first value in the stated order (e.g. studyUUID) is effective, the rest ignored.
